      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 60 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 60 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>節，亨。苦節不可貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Jie intimates that (under its conditions) there will be progress and attainment. (But) if the regulations (which it prescribes) be severe and difficult, they cannot be permanent.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
