      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 60 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：不出戶庭，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject not quitting the courtyard outside his door. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
