      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：不出門庭，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject not quitting the courtyard inside his gate. There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
