      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 60 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：不節若，則嗟若，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows its subject with no appearance of observing the (proper) regulations, in which case we shall see him lamenting. But there will be no one to blame (but himself).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
