      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：安節，亨。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject quietly and naturally (attentive to all) regulations. There will be progress and success.</seg>
