      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 60 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：甘節，吉；往有尚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject sweetly and acceptably enacting his regulations. There will be good fortune. The onward progress with them will afford ground for admiration.</seg>
      </tuv>
